## 🛠️ 10. Admin Dashboard

### 🎯 Goal

Content control, analytics, and system health.

---

### Sidebar Navigation

* Dashboard
* Stories
* Riddles
* Users
* AI Settings
* Analytics

---

### Story Management UI

* Story list (table)
* Filters (difficulty, age)
* Create / Edit story form

  * Title
  * Content editor
  * Media upload
  * Linked riddles

---

### Riddle Management UI

* Riddle editor

  * Question
  * Correct answer
  * Accepted variations
  * Difficulty tag
  * Hint strategy

* AI Assist Button:

  * Suggest hints
  * Validate difficulty

---

### Analytics UI

* Most failed riddles
* Drop-off points
* Average solve time

AI suggestions appear as **info cards**, not alerts.

